text: Ranabhat () is a Chhetri surname of Khas community of Nepal. It's derived from the title Ranawat. Present Ranabhat of Nepal claim descent Rajputs of Rajasthan. Recent research has showed that these claims may be spurious. Notable Ranabhat includes: *Eknath Ranabhat, Former member of Parliament of Nepal *Taranath Ranabhat, Former speaker at Nepalese Parliament == References == Category:Nepali-language surnames
